					"english": "Are you good? (to male)",
					"transliteration": "Enta kwayyes?"
				},
				{
					"arabic": "أنتِ كويسة؟",
					"english": "Are you good? (to female)",
					"transliteration": "Enti kwayyesa?"
				}
			]
		}
	],
	"culturalNotes": [
